{
  "id": "L3N",
  "title": "At the Caf\u00e9",
  "description": "Learn how to order drinks and snacks at a Dutch caf\u00e9.",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Welcome! In this lesson, you'll learn how to order at a Dutch caf\u00e9 ('het caf\u00e9'). The Dutch love their coffee and 'gezelligheid' (coziness)!"
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V01",
      "data": {
        "Het caf\u00c3\u00a9": "The caf\u00e9"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V02",
      "data": {
        "De koffie": "The coffee"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V03",
      "data": {
        "De thee": "The tea"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V04",
      "data": {
        "Het bier": "The beer"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3N_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Mag ik de menukaart?",
        "meaning": "May I have the menu?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3N_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ik wil graag een koffie.",
        "meaning": "I would like a coffee."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3N_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "met melk",
        "meaning": "with milk"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3N_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "met suiker",
        "meaning": "with sugar"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L3N_S01",
      "title": "Ordering a Drink",
      "setting": "You sit down at a cozy caf\u00e9. The waiter comes to take your order.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Ask for the menu",
          "chatbot_message": "Goedemiddag. Wat wilt u drinken?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Order coffee with milk",
          "chatbot_message": "Natuurlijk. Met melk en suiker?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Receive your drink",
          "chatbot_message": "Komt eraan. E\u00e9n koffie met melk."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V05",
      "data": {
        "Het broodje kaas": "The cheese sandwich"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V06",
      "data": {
        "De appeltaart": "The apple pie"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V07",
      "data": {
        "De bitterballen": "The bitterballen (Dutch snack)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3N_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Wat raadt u aan?",
        "meaning": "What do you recommend?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3N_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Ik neem de appeltaart.",
        "meaning": "I'll take the apple pie."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L3N_S02",
      "title": "Ordering Food",
      "setting": "The waiter returns and asks if you want something to eat.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Ask for a recommendation",
          "chatbot_message": "Wilt u er ook iets bij eten?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Order apple pie",
          "chatbot_message": "Onze appeltaart is heel lekker. Of misschien een broodje kaas?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Receive confirmation",
          "chatbot_message": "Goede keuze! Een appeltaart erbij."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V08",
      "data": {
        "De rekening": "The bill"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L3N_V09",
      "data": {
        "Gezellig": "Cozy / nice atmosphere"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3N_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Mag ik de rekening?",
        "meaning": "May I have the bill?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L3N_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Het was heel lekker.",
        "meaning": "It was very tasty."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L3N_S03",
      "title": "Paying and Leaving",
      "setting": "You've finished your coffee and apple pie. Time to pay.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Compliment the food",
          "chatbot_message": "Heeft het gesmaakt?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask for the bill",
          "chatbot_message": "Fijn om te horen! Anders nog iets?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Say goodbye",
          "chatbot_message": "Dat is dan 8 euro 50. Dank u wel en tot ziens!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Lekker gedaan! You can now confidently order at a Dutch caf\u00e9. In the next lesson, we'll learn how to ask for directions!"
